<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
  <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #5741AC;">Multiplication Connect Four</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-700">Use the factor controls to choose a number and mark the board. First player to connect four-in-a-row horizontally, vertically, or diagonally is the winner.</p>
  </div>

